      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay i understand that. but the pain is getting really bad and i dont want to go to the hospital for just a headache if i can help it. can i take a little bit of advil/ibuprofen just to take the edge off? like maybe one pill? it shouldn't be a huge deal if it's just a small amount.",
